If we say that the Qian and Kun hexagrams are the guiding principles for those who aspire to greatness,

7
00:00:17,054 --> 00:00:22,048
So, the Tun Hexagram is the fundamental principle for the beginning of every person's journey that we'll all encounter!

8
00:00:22,048 --> 00:00:27,012
So, if you've ever wondered why everything just feels off when you first enter the workforce or join a new company,

9
